summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5447 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 3, H. S. Turner Park Addition, being the alley between 25th Avenue North and 26th Avenue North, from East Newton Street to East Lynn Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 68692, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
